---
// scene 1 · catalog matrix — the model catalog as a living surface. A grid of
// cells (opacity as noise) stands in for models × providers. A scanline sweeps
// on a schedule; changes caught in the pass blip accent over their cells.
// Standalone 7s loop; the reel version gates this to its 18s window.
---

